      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SON OF MANADO (1) was unwanted in betting last start but proved too quick with an all-the-way win over 400m at this track in a Novice race, scoring by half a length (22.90). Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Will go close again if runs up to latest. MANX MAGIC (6) has found the minor placings here at last couple of runs, finishing second last time beaten 1.75 lengths (22.85). Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Hard to beat again. AKRON ROCKET (3) was strongly fancied last time on the back of a win two back but could only manage third (23.19) at this track. Boasts two wins from five starts out of this box. Expected to feature again. AVATAR OF FUN (2) was prominent throughout when successful last start. Sure to run well again.",
